2019年10月，Canva宣布增資8,500萬澳洲元，估值達32億澳洲元，並推出企業版服務。<ref name="tc" /><ref name="Anny"/>同年12月，該平台宣布向學校和其他教育機構推出免費服務Canva for Education，旨在促進學生和教師的交流。<ref>{{cite news |last1=Hennessy |first1=James |title=Canva has announced a slew of new products, including a video editing tool and an education offering |url=https://www.businessinsider.com.au/canva-new-products-canva-video-apps-2019-12 |work=Business Insider Australia |date=2019-12-06 |language=en |accessdate=2021-04-06 |archive-date=2020-06-19 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200619195450/https://www.businessinsider.com.au/canva-new-products-canva-video-apps-2019-12 |dead-url=no }}</ref>2020年6月，該平台宣布與印刷公司[[聯邦快遞金考|聯邦快遞金考]]合作<ref>{{Cite news |url=https://techcrunch.com/2020/06/16/canva-design-platform-partners-with-fedex-office-as-it-pushes-further-into-the-u-s/ |title=Canva design platform partners with FedEx Office as it pushes further into the US |last=Crook |first=Jordan |date=2020-06-17 |work=TechCrunch |language=en |accessdate=2021-04-06 |archive-date=2021-01-26 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210126231440/https://techcrunch.com/2020/06/16/canva-design-platform-partners-with-fedex-office-as-it-pushes-further-into-the-u-s/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>，次月再與辦公用品公司[[歐迪辦公|歐迪辦公]]合作。<ref>{{Cite news |url=https://www.bloomberg.com/press-releases/2020-07-16/office-depot-enhances-print-services-portfolio-with-new-graphic-design-solutions-powered-by-canva |title=Office Depot Enhances Print Services Portfolio with New Graphic Design Solutions Powered by Canva |date=2020-07-16 |work=Bloomberg |language=en-US |accessdate=2021-04-06 |archive-date=2020-07-21 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200721003640/https://www.bloomberg.com/press-releases/2020-07-16/office-depot-enhances-print-services-portfolio-with-new-graphic-design-solutions-powered-by-canva |dead-url=no }}</ref>截至2020年6月，Canva的公司估值已升至60億澳洲元。<ref>{{Cite news |url=https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2020-06-22/australia-s-canva-raises-60-million-at-6-billion-value |title=Australia's Canva Startup Almost Doubles Valuation to $6 Billion |first=Crystal |date=2020-06-22 |work=Bloomberg |last2=Roof |first2=Katie |language=en-US |last3=Tan |first3=Gillian |last4=Lee |first4=Yoolim |last1=Tse |accessdate=2021-04-06 |archive-date=2021-02-22 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210222185305/https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2020-06-22/australia-s-canva-raises-60-million-at-6-billion-value |dead-url=no }}</ref>

